name: Peacock Feathers
description:
Red and green leaves move across a blue background, clustering up into waves and sheafs. A bit of a swarming term crept in, driving the velocity of things up to the limit of damping and breaking the structures free of the underlying substrate. The stationary trails in the blue background show how the moving swarms have modified the local parameters of the simulation. / @ngutten
